structure.unit: PAYMENT, COLLECTION, AND REFUND OF TAXES

law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 73, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1994. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 183, sec. 4, effective July 13 ,1990. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4239f.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Collection of delinquent and omitted tax bills -- Percentage to county attorney for collections.
